{"tid":1550834,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解當年可以告得入黑警朱經緯同暗角7警","createTime":"2019-09-07T18:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T19:15:55.000Z","uid":277536,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"843155c3c5cc5ab43011974aefb68875eb1cb413","tid":1550834,"uid":277536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:00:07.000Z","msg":"當年可以告得入黑警朱經緯 同 暗角7警？<br />\n<br />\n點解呢幾個月大量黑警濫權打人，有哂影片都可以無事？<br />\n<br />\n到底邊part唔同佐？？？<br />\n黑警務署？ 律政司？？<br />\n<br />\n當年到底如何告到上法庭？？？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e115f28136f20b0ed8aeec0b0064bfc92b755bd9","tid":1550834,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:00:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d8d1684e5121b0c60a713c0434643b8a64bd0c5","tid":1550834,"uid":277536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3adb4c28cc9f6d878f9a09b0a536400fb7e084","tid":1550834,"uid":230104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:04:54.000Z","msg":"因為有原告，而家果班畀人打完怕事、唔想搞大、無撚用<br />\n<br />\n如果個個都好似曾健超咁開記招展示傷勢+報警（程序）"},{"pid":"3f05a1d8ea5b5e41713a6809d251e1fc7a26c570","tid":1550834,"uid":3549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:12:12.000Z","msg":"係香港變左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇no. 冇樣 <br />\n否認所有事實<br />\n投訴無門<br />\n隨時原告變被告<br />\n<br />\n點告，依家警察大過一切"},{"pid":"8c5de06db70ba74c00dc100b7879c3619cf96a7f","tid":1550834,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:15:39.000Z","msg":"熱門一個908嘅post都冇？入嚟推兩野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f7d3d9c01a84fbd00cefb80aa60585bfdb459f41","tid":1550834,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:16:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">打咗好多場官司，雙方交戰好耐，黑狗想保護自己友不合法打人，同最重要隻朱狗咁岩到退休要離開狗隊</span></span>"},{"pid":"1013feeb7a39575b7e6a057c7d99c3253c8a7e79","tid":1550834,"uid":309002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:19:54.000Z","msg":"因為當事人企出黎<br />\n有議員幫<br />\n而家好難講 未必敢出黎吿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7e4b75732b82447e298cc5362077136f70a057","tid":1550834,"uid":314830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f05a1d8ea5b5e41713a6809d251e1fc7a26c570","tid":1550834,"uid":3549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:12:12.000Z","msg":"係香港變左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇no. 冇樣 <br />\n否認所有事實<br />\n投訴無門<br />\n隨時原告變被告<br />\n<br />\n點告，依家警察大過一切"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:15:55.000Z","msg":"x2<br />\n<br />\n仲要有林鄭保住"}]}